      <context>
         <note id="note_upr_ppt_5gc" type="note">
            <p>The engine will not start unless the transmission directional control lever is in the
        NEUTRAL position.</p>
         </note>
         <fig id="fig_ogn_qpt_5gc">
            <image href="media/image756a.png"
                   id="image_rgn_qpt_5gc"
                   placement="inline"/>
         </fig>
         <p>Typical Example</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Engage the parking brake, if not already engaged.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Place the transmission directional control lever in NEUTRAL position.</p>
            <p>
               <note type="notice">
                  <p>When you restart the engine after turning off it, wait 4 to 5 seconds and restart
            it to protect the starter.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
